Description:
read a report_metric config yaml file

Usage: read_metric_config [-help]
                          <filename> [-format {html excel text vivid}]

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
<filename>                          # filename to read metric config from
                                    # (string, required)
-format {html excel text vivid}     # config for specified report_metric format
                                    # (enum, optional)